descript.abstract: Linear features produced from the GEONAMES_ANNO_HYDRO annotation feature class representing the positioning, angles and curvature of the annotation labels. These lines may be used as substitutes for annotation in software or applications that cannot work with true annotation. To duplicate the effect of the annotation, these lines should be displayed with no color or thickness, but they should be labeled and displayed with the 1:25,000 Hydrography layers.
